## 发表评论 [/sendComment]


### 返回数据格式

+ data - 值为ok表示成功，其他失败 

### 发表评论 [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

  + Body

    {
      "userId": "afdaf",
      "id": "DA05BA8E06BB410F9B86ACC14100E6F2",
      "type": "event",
      "content": "打雷啦，下雨啦，收衣服啦。"
    }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  
  + Body
  
    {
      "data": "ok",
      "code": 0
    }



## 对评论点赞 [/likeComment]


### 返回数据格式

+ data - 值为ok表示成功，其他失败 

### 对评论点赞 [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

  + Body

    {
      "userId": "afdaf",
      "id": "1",
      "type": "event",
    }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  
  + Body
  
    {
      "data": "ok",
      "code": 0
    }
